title: Apply Now!! Don't Miss out!
posting_body: Welcome to your new home at Harvard Square in North Dallas, Texas!
Feel at home with our refreshing swimming pool, convenient 24-hour fitness center, and two lighted tennis courts.
Only ten minutes away from downtown Dallas, you will find unique downtown shopping, dining and entertainment to satisfy your every need.
In addition, we offer various amenities to make your new home even more convenient and spacious!
